	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "According to her hagiography, she was martyred \"in the city Rome under king Alexander in the fourth\n                 year of his reign\" (በሀገረ፡ ሮሜ፡ ላዕለ፡ እለ፡ እስክንድሮስ፡ ንጉሥ፡ በራብዕ፡ ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡), which\n               might lead to her identification with Tatiana of Rome." .
